snippet.title: Homeworld: Vast Reaches - Official Launch Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Get a new look at battles and more from Homeworld: Vast Reaches in this latest trailer for the upcoming action strategy game. Homeworld: Vast Reaches is available now on Meta Quest, and it is coming to SteamVR on November 14, 2024. Immerse yourself in a bold new story in the beloved Homeworld saga that brings real-time strategic space battles to VR. Your fleet is at your fingertips in this all-new game where you can execute strategic attacks on your enemies from any direction or angle.
